          "reviewBody": "Worst school negative star. Teachers speak in Hindi .aaya take care of kids . principle ke alag tasaon hai unko parents se milna nahi hai .please don't take admission in this school it's a disaster in the name of school. Bhaiya anpadh rakh Lena bachhe ko par is school me mat padhana . Worst into infinity",
          "publisher": {
