          "reviewBody": "I put my son in this school recently after reading the reviews I thought it is a good school..but it's my worste experience I never think that not only for 1 point so many things are not good first is teachers are speaking Hindi with the students but at the time of admission they said communication would be in English so no learning of another language.second is few kids are speaking proper villager language in the class that is worste thing and third is the caretaker in the class speaks very harsh and proper villager language with the kids it's my personal experience.i cant say anything about others.one more thing the teacher who used to come in the bus with the kids never greet the kids.",
